text: Köln-Chorweiler Nord is a railway station situated at Chorweiler, Cologne in western Germany. It is served by the S11 line of the Rhine-Ruhr S-Bahn at 20-minute intervals from Monday to Friday and at 30-minute intervals on the weekend. == References == Category:S11 (Rhine-Ruhr S-Bahn) Category:Railway stations in Cologne Category:Railway stations located underground in Germany Category:Rhine-Ruhr S-Bahn stations Category:Railway stations in Germany opened in 1977 Category:Chorweiler
